{"title": "果部·枸橼", "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "果部·枸橼"}, {"type": "text", "value": "释名"}, {"type": "text", "value": "香橼、佛手柑。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "气味"}, {"type": "text", "value": "（皮瓤）辛、酸、无毒。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "主治"}, {"type": "text", "value": "煮酒饮，治痰气咳嗽，煎汤，治心下气痛。"}], "index": 572}